• Seeking experienced Solidity developer with 3+ years of hands-on experience in building decentralized applications on Ethereum; 
• Must have a strong understanding of smart contract best practices and security protocols;
• Prior experience with Web3 development stack (e.g., Truffle, Ganache) and familiarity with testing frameworks (e.g., Truffle Test) a plus;
• Bachelor's degree in Computer Science or related field required; 
• Open to both full-time and contract arrangements; 
• Must have ability to work remotely with minimal supervision; 
• Start date: ASAP but ideally 2 weeks from receipt of perfect candidate.

• Senior QA Engineer with 4+ years of experience in automated testing using Selenium and Cypress; 
• Strong Java skills with proficiency in JUnit framework; 
• Experience working on multiple agile projects, with ability to prioritize and manage testing efforts;
• Familiarity with Continuous Integration/Continuous Deployment (CI/CD) pipelines a plus;
• Must have at least 2+ years of experience working remotely or in a flexible work environment;
• Full-time employment only; ideally start date within the next 60 days;
• US citizen with active Secret clearance.

• Expert-level proficiency in Go (12+ years) and/or Rust (8+ years); 5-7 years of experience with Python/Django; 
• Strong understanding of RESTful architecture, microservices, and cloud infrastructure (AWS/GCP/ Azure);
• 3+ years of hands-on experience with containerization (Docker), CI/CD pipelines (Jenkins/GitLab), and testing frameworks (Pytest/unittest);
• Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail; ability to work independently and collaboratively within a distributed team;
• Possess strong code organization, design, and development skills, with the ability to effectively mentor junior developers;
• Valid US security clearance (TS/SCI) or willingness to obtain; 
• Comfortable working in an agile environment and collaborating with cross-functional teams; 
• Experience with GitHub/Bitbucket for version control management; 
• Strong analytical and technical skills with a strong focus on scalability, reliability, and maintainability;
• Availability to start within 60 days.

• Senior Mobile Developer with 4+ years’ experience in iOS development using Swift and Objective-C;
• Strong understanding of iOS architecture, memory management, and multi-threading concepts;
• Proficient in Xcode, SwiftUI, Core Data, and Firebase;
• Experience with CI/CD pipelines, JIRA, and Agile methodologies;
• Ability to lead by example, mentoring junior team members;
• Availability for immediate start;

• Seeking Senior Software Engineer with 5+ years of experience in C and C++ development for embedded systems, specifically working with RTOS and Nucleus;
• Hands-on expertise with firmware development, preferably on Altera/ Intel-based FPGAs;
• Strong understanding of concurrent programming, scheduling, and synchronization concepts;
• Experience with version control systems like Git and Subversion;
• Proven track record in debugging complex software issues, particularly using Eclipse-based environments;
• Willingness to learn and adapt to new technologies, tools, and methodologies as needed.
• Location flexibility: open to discussing either an on-site or remote work arrangement; full-time employment with competitive benefits offered.

• Seeking experienced SRE with 5+ years of hands-on experience in designing and implementing scalable infrastructure solutions using Google Cloud Platform, AWS, or Azure;
• Proven track record of improving system reliability, with expertise in observability, monitoring, and Log aggregation tools (e.g., Prometheus, Grafana, ELK);
• Strong understanding of containerization (Docker) and orchestration (Kubernetes) technologies for deploying and managing microservices;
• Familiarity with cloud-native applications, service mesh architectures, and API gateways a plus;
• Excellent problem-solving skills, with the ability to work independently as well as part of a collaborative team;
• Bachelor's or Master's degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field;
